text: The Liwale round-snouted worm lizard (Loveridgea ionidesii) is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is found in Tanzania. ==References== Category:Loveridgea Category:Endemic fauna of Tanzania Category:Reptiles of Tanzania Category:Reptiles described in 1950 Category:Taxa named by James Clarence Battersby
title: Liwale round-snouted worm lizard
